      "content": "that's a huge relief to hear. i been feeling like i was crazy for even looking into this.\n\nif i'm going to take this to the UN or even the ICC, what's the first step to actually force them to look at this? since they basically scrubbed us from the map, i assume there's some kind of specialized legal procedure for \"reconstituting\" a lost sovereign entity. do i need to establish a provisional government first to have standing in these courts?",
